Endpoint and request data
To Update Task
http://127.0.0.1:8000/update-task/17/
{
    "status":2,
    "description":"carry",
    "id" : 2
}
Only Assignee will be able to update the task
where is the id of user wanted to make request
to get task assigned
http://127.0.0.1:8000/task-assigned/
{
    "id" : 2
}
To get created task
http://127.0.0.1:8000/get-task-created/
{
    "id":1
}
To Create Task
http://127.0.0.1:8000/create-task/
 {
    "name": "Task Name",
    "description": "Task Description",
    "status": 0,
    "created_by": 1,
    "assignee":[2,5]
}
only manager will be able to create task